    "en": [
        {
            "text": "Today you can purchase single tickets for bus and tram, and eventually you will find all tickets in the app.\n",
            "type": "text"
        },
        {
            "text": "The tickets only applies to public transport that is part of the public transport system in Trøndelag county.",
            "type": "text"
        },
        {
            "text": "The ticket must be purchased before boarding.",
            "type": "heading"
        },
        {
            "text": "You do not need to show the ticket on green city buses and tram in the Trondheim area. Outside the Trondheim area, you must show the ticket to the driver or crew.\n",
            "type": "text"
        },
        {
            "text": "The ticket is valid for boarding until it expires, that is, as long as the countdown lasts and in the zone(s) you have purchased the ticket for.\n",
            "type": "text"
        },
        {
            "text": "Travel in one zone: 1 hour and 30 minutes",
            "type": "text"
        },
        {
            "text": "Travel in two zones: 2 hours and 30 minutes",
            "type": "text"
        },
        {
            "text": "Travel in three zones: 3 hours and 30 minutes",
            "type": "text"
        },
        {
            "text": "Travel in four zones: 4 hours and 30 minutes\n",
            "type": "text"
        },
        {
            "text": "Please contact the driver if you need a transfer ticket.",
